cember, the Christmas Fair<br \/>takes place here, in an enjoyable atmosphere.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #0070c0;\">Timisoara<br \/>is the largest city in the Western part of Romania, a vibrant center of<br \/>science and culture, as well as an industrial pole, together with the<br \/>city of Arad, 50 km to the North.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #0070c0;\">Participants<br \/>to the Conference may visit the historical center, with Unirii\u2019s<br \/>Square, enjoy the local restaurants and cuisine, in a multi-cultural<br \/>environment that has led Timisoara to be elected as <a href=\"https:\/\/timisoara2023.eu\/en\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">2023 European Capital of Culture<\/a>.<br \/><br \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000080;\"><strong>We wish you a delightful stay in this hospitable part of Romania!<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>\u00a0<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/3om-group-optomechatronics.ro\/advances-in-3om-conference-2023\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/timisoara1-300x198.jpg\" alt=\"timisoara1\" width=\"323\" height=\"213\" \/><\/td>\n<td>\u00a0<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/3om-group-optomechatronics.ro\/advances-in-3om-conference-2023\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/timisoara2-300x198.jpg\" alt=\"timisoara2\" width=\"314\" height=\"207\" \/><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/3om-group-optomechatronics.ro\/advances-in-3om-conference-2023\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/timisoara3-300x123.jpg\" alt=\"timisoara3\" width=\"317\" height=\"130\" \/><br \/><br \/><br \/><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ec58244 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"ec58244\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.de